      <p><strong>Israel Pulla</strong> and <strong>Adrian Santamaria</strong> are two young entrepreneurs with deep roots in the Latino community and a passion for helping local businesses grow and thrive. Drawing from their own experiences growing up in blue-collar households and working in hospitality and service sectors, they created Ocean Avenue Consulting to bring strategy and hands-on support to small businesses facing seasonal booms.</p>
      <p>With firsthand knowledge of the challenges faced by family-run shops, restaurants, and summer-driven businesses, they provide practical, results-driven solutions while preserving the heart and culture of local enterprises.</p>
